videos.headline: West breaks free for 31-yard run
videos.description: Braeden West bursts through the line for a 31-yard run.

videos.headline: Hicks finds Sutton in traffic for 6-yard TD pass
videos.description: Ben Hicks completes a pass to Courtland Sutton who finds the end zone for a 6-yard  touchdown.

videos.headline: McLean zips past SMU's defense for 64-yard TD
videos.description: Bryant Shirreffs completes a short pass to Aaron McLean who takes it the distance for a  64-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Jones sprints free for 25-yard TD run
videos.description: SMU's Xavier Jones bolts down the sideline for a 25-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Newsome's  catch and run puts SMU in opposing territory
videos.description: Bryant Shirreffs completes a pass to Arkeel Newsome for a 47 yard gain.

videos.headline: Quinn's TD grab helps extend SMU's lead
videos.description: Ben Hicks connects with Trey Quinn for a 21- yard touchdown in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Skanes makes impressive bobbling catch for UCONN 1st down
videos.description: Quayvon Skanes tips the ball to himself and makes the catch for a 9 yard gain.

videos.headline: Hopkins' TD run cuts into SMU's lead
videos.description: UCONN's Nate Hopkins sprints for a two-yard touchdown run in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Beals big catch and run puts UCONN  in the red zone
videos.description: Bryant Shirreffs completes short pass to Tyraiq Beals who cuts up field for 47-yards into the red zone.

videos.headline: Hicks finds Quinn for TD to extend SMU's lead
videos.description: Ben Hicks connects with Trey Quinn for a 15- yard touchdown reception to keep SMU ahead.

videos.headline: Shirreffs hits Dixon deep to bring UCONN within two
videos.description: UCONN's Bryant Shirreffs throws a strike to  Keyion Dixon for a 59-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Davis's 2-point grab ties the game
videos.description: Bryant Shirreffs finds Tyler  Davis in the end zone for the two-point conversion.

videos.headline: SMU retakes lead with Hicks TD pass
videos.description: Ben Hicks finds Courtland Sutton for a 34-yard touchdown pass in the 4th quarter.

videos.headline: Becker blocks punt to put SMU at mid field
videos.description: Ryan Becker leaps up to block the UCONN punt, to set up SMU with good field position.

videos.headline: Freeman's short TD run extends SMU's lead
videos.description: Ke'Mon Freeman sprints up the middle for a 3-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: West's 25-yard TD run secures SMU victory
videos.description: Braeden West jukes UCONN defenders and sprints for a SMU touchdown.
